        "# 3008ICT Deep Learning – Assignment 2\n",
        "## Recurrent Neural Networks for IMDb Sentiment Analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "Implements **Vanilla RNN**, **LSTM**, and **Bidirectional LSTM (BRNN)** on the IMDb dataset (25k train / 25k test) in PyTorch."
      ]
