          "text": [
            "LSTMClassifier(\n",
            "  (embedding): Embedding(20002, 128, padding_idx=0)\n",
            "  (lstm): LSTM(128, 256, num_layers=2, batch_first=True, dropout=0.5)\n",
            "  (dropout): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)\n",
            "  (fc): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=2, bias=True)\n",
            ")\n",
            "Epoch 1/5 | Train 0.6934/0.5025 | Test 0.6933/0.5047 | 17.2s\n",
            "Epoch 2/5 | Train 0.6922/0.5060 | Test 0.6938/0.5036 | 17.2s\n",
