            "Epoch 4/5 | Train 0.6893/0.5147 | Test 0.6965/0.5011 | 17.3s\n",
            "Epoch 5/5 | Train 0.6881/0.5155 | Test 0.7005/0.5036 | 17.3s\n",
            "\n",
